00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:48.510 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Robert Patrick: Well, the Library

00:00:48.510 --> 00:00:51.600 position:97%
of Congress Veterans History Project has been an ongoing effort here

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:52.940
since 2000.

00:00:52.940 --> 00:00:57.210 position:97%
The purpose of this project is to get the human experience of war,

00:00:59.720 --> 00:01:02.100 position:66%
