00:01:15.090 --> 00:01:18.620 position:98%
tell their story and become a part of what has become a very rich

00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:22.070 position:63%
and used collection here at the Library.

00:01:22.070 --> 00:01:24.560 position:97%
It's gonna be able to capture those from World War I all the way

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.110
up to the current conflict.

00:01:26.110 --> 00:01:28.850 position:97%
And we do it primarily through oral histories and the collection

00:01:28.850 --> 00:01:31.230 position:70%
of materials that veterans have sent into us.

