00:01:59.170 --> 00:02:02.040 position:66%
&gt;&gt; Gary Sinise: And just send it into you?

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:03.170 position:97%
&gt;&gt; Robert Patrick: - and send it into us, and they become a part

00:02:03.170 --> 00:02:04.120
