00:04:52.060 --> 00:04:55.920 position:92%
Also, in his collection, there's some very touching letters

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:57.510
from Irving Berlin to him.

00:04:57.510 --> 00:05:00.990 position:61%
This is Irving Berlin at a medical ward

00:05:00.990 --> 00:05:05.070 position:67%
